# Project Context

## Overview
This project uses the Ralph Loop pattern. Each agent instance works on exactly one task from tasks.md, then exits. A new agent is spawned with fresh context.

## Conventions
- Tasks are in tasks.md, marked with `- [ ]` (incomplete) or `- [x]` (complete)
- Work on only the FIRST incomplete task
- Commit after each successful task
- Document learnings below after each iteration

